  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK550">
<l>kolaiyiṟ koṭiyārai vēntoṟuttal paiṅkūḻ </l>
<l> kaḷaikaṭ ṭataṉōṭu nēr</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For a king to punish criminals with death, is like pulling up the weeds in the green corn.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
